TokenV = ref object
  tok*: Token
  case tags*: TokenVTags
  of TVNormal:
      nil

  of TVSVal:
      s*: string

  of TVFval:
      f*: float
      ftag*: FTag

  of TVIVal:
      i*: int
      itag*: ITag

  of TVStr:
      str*: string
      enc*: uint8
